metadata.name: Alive
metadata.description: Encrypted by the ways of live that the hyper-city have developed , virtual entities have took the control of our environments, our fragmented gazes can not distinguish the truth, immersed by the dystopian merge of virtual and natural worlds, we have been compel to flee to the meta-verse, creating our "own reality", a utopia, feed by our actions and transactions (data), shaping by the rules of control dictated by the tyrants of data
